title: Yankees clinch playoff spot after 2-year absence, top Boston
text:
> Sports Yankees clinch playoff spot after 2-year absence, top Boston New York Yankees starting pitcher Luis Severino, center, sprays teammates as the Yankees celebrated their 4-1 win over the Boston Red Sox that allowed them to clinch a wild card berth in the playoffs after a baseball game in New York, Thursday, Oct. 1, 2015. (AP Photo/Kathy Willens)
